"media-ratio--full-width-image","imageAllignment":"center","jcr:lastModified":"Fri Oct 18 2019 13:10:30 GMT+0530","desktopImage":"/content/dam/dbi/19F_LOWRES/Something Blue/BRoll_Veil2_SMTHNG_BLUE_v3_Q3_19F.jpg","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/image"},"rich_text_with_light":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","header":"alterations","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Fri Oct 11 2019 13:26:19 GMT-0400","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:45:18 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/rich-text-with-light-header","rteDesc":"<p>Each David's Bridal location has on-site alterations experts so you can personalize your dress and get the perfect fit.</p>\r\n","textIsRich":"true"},"faq_container":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Fri Oct 11 2019 13:27:04 GMT-0400","jcr:lastModified":"Fri Oct 11 2019 13:27:04 GMT-0400","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-container","parsys":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","sling:resourceType":"wcm/foundation/components/responsivegrid","faq_question":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Fri Oct 11 2019 13:31:03 GMT-0400","title":"customize your gown by adding your own personal touches!","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:45:35 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question","parsys":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","sling:resourceType":"wcm/foundation/components/responsivegrid"}},"faq_question_729979204":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:47:40 GMT+0530","title":"schedule your fitting at the time you purchase your gown or dress","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:47:52 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question"},"faq_question_1842711370":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:48:23 GMT+0530","title":"why have your gown altered at david's bridal?","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:48:28 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question","parsys":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","sling:resourceType":"wcm/foundation/components/parsys","image":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","titleTag":"image","mobileImage":"/content/dam/dbi/19F_LOWRES/Something Blue/9SWG772_IVYCHAMP_SIG_SMTHNG_BLUE_Q3_19F.jpg","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","altText":"image","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:48:40 GMT+0530","classVariation":"media-ratio--half-height-image","imageAllignment":"start","jcr:lastModified":"Fri Oct 18 2019 15:04:03 GMT+0530","desktopImage":"/content/dam/dbi/19F_LOWRES/Something Blue/BRoll_Veil1_SMTHNG_BLUE_v2_Q3_19F.jpg","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/image"},"faq_question_text":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:49:32 GMT+0530","text":"<p>David's Bridal gowns are designed to fit. In fact, we offer the best fit in the industry, backed by more than 60 years of experience. But even the best designed gowns still need some adjustment. No one has more experience with detailed bridal garments than our expert professionals who work exclusively on tailoring our attire. Each of our alterations specialists are trained to achieve the fit that's ideal for your body type and dress style.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>And when you bring your gown to David's Bridal, you know it will be returned on time in pristine condition. We guarantee the quality of the altered garment will be equal to, or better than, its original quality. Yes, the process of altering gowns and special occasion dresses is complex, but our specialists are expert at making any adjustments required, from the most minor to the most intricate. <a title=\"Book\" href=\"#\" target=\"_self\">Book an appointment.</a></p>\r\n","jcr:lastModified":"Fri Oct 18 2019 15:03:38 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question-text","textIsRich":"true"}}},"faq_question_84277973":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:52:02 GMT+0530","title":"what you should expect at your first fitting appointment","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:52:07 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question"},"faq_question_233996345":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:52:24 GMT+0530","title":"complimentary pressing","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:52:30 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question"}}},"image_76109915":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","titleTag":"Title Tag","mobileImage":"/content/dam/dbi/19F_LOWRES/MISC/GRP1_MSILVER_JWLY_MAY_Q319.jpg","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","altText":"Alternative Text","jcr:created":"Fri Oct 11 2019 14:32:08 GMT-0400","classVariation":"media-ratio--half-width-image","imageAllignment":"start","jcr:lastModified":"Fri Oct 18 2019 15:05:00 GMT+0530","desktopImage":"/content/dam/dbi/19F_LOWRES/Something Blue/SWG823_IVYCASHMERE_SIG_SMTHNG_BLUE_Q3_19F.jpg","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/image"},"rich_text_with_light_1364669998":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","header":"Store Services","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Fri Oct 11 2019 14:30:47 GMT-0400","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:55:46 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/rich-text-with-light-header","rteDesc":"<p>In additional to expert alterations, our stores can help you coordinate your wedding with dyeable shoes and handbags, tuxedos, invitations, and more. We also offer professional gown cleaning and preservation for after the big day. Payment options include the David's Bridal credit card and layaway.&nbsp;</p>\r\n","textIsRich":"true"},"faq_container_2116460837":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:54:55 GMT+0530","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:54:55 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-container","parsys":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","sling:resourceType":"wcm/foundation/components/parsys","faq_question":{"jcr:primaryType":"nt:unstructured","jcr:createdBy":"admin","jcr:lastModifiedBy":"admin","jcr:created":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:55:02 GMT+0530","title":"how much will alterations cost?","jcr:lastModified":"Mon Oct 14 2019 16:55:13 GMT+0530","sling:resourceType":"dbi/components/content/faq-question"}}}}}}}